Welcome to cs_gmw_lis (lost in space). 

2 hostages have been captured by the T's and transported aboard a star destroyer somewhere in our solar system. The CT's are on hot pursuit in a space shuttle and have just caught up with the star destroyer. CT's join the game in the chasing space shuttle just as they are preparing to teleport aboard the star destroyer.

Counter-Terrorists:- Board the star destroyer, remove the terrorist threat, rescue the hostages and escort them back to the transporter room on the lower deck level.

Terrorists:- Eliminate the Counter Terrorists and stop them from taking your valuable hostages.Â 

Hope you enjoy this map.

[GMW]Keeshna
